#: urpm/cli/main.py:577
msgid "Create a minimal Docker/Podman image for RPM builds"
msgstr "Créer une image Docker/Podman minimale pour les compilations RPM"

#: urpm/cli/main.py:579
msgid ""
"Create a minimal Mageia Docker/Podman image for RPM builds.\n"
"\n"
"The image contains a minimal system with urpmi configured to use\n"
"the official Mageia mirrors. Use with 'urpm build' for isolated builds.\n"
"\n"
"Profiles are loaded from:\n"
"  /usr/share/urpm/profiles/*.yaml (system)\n"
"  /etc/urpm/profiles/*.yaml (local additions)\n"
"\n"
"Examples:\n"
"  urpm mkimage --release 10 --tag mageia:10-build\n"
"  urpm mkimage --release 10 --tag mageia:10-ci --profile ci\n"
"  urpm mkimage --release cauldron --tag mageia:cauldron-build --runtime podman\n"
msgstr ""
"Crée une image Docker/Podman Mageia minimale pour les compilations RPM.\n"
"\n"
"L'image contient un système minimal avec urpmi configuré pour utiliser\n"
"les miroirs officiels de Mageia. À utiliser avec 'urpm build' pour des compilations isolées.\n"
"\n"
"Les profils sont chargés depuis :\n"
"  /usr/share/urpm/profiles/*.yaml (système)\n"
"  /etc/urpm/profiles/*.yaml (ajouts locaux)\n"
"\n"
"Exemples :\n"
"  urpm mkimage --release 10 --tag mageia:10-build\n"
"  urpm mkimage --release 10 --tag mageia:10-ci --profile ci\n"
"  urpm mkimage --release cauldron --tag mageia:cauldron-build --runtime podman\n"

